title.en: "24-ten" to Konyaku Hakisareta Reijou wa, Ringoku no Outaishi ni Kanpeki na Hanayome to Aisareru
Konyaku Hakisareta "Kuuki" na Watashi, Nariagari no Danna-sama ni Totsugimashita.
Enzai Reijou wa Shinjitai - Ginpatsu ga Fukitsu to Iwarete Konyaku Hakisareta Shishaku Reijou wa Ansatsu Kizoku ni Dekiaisarete Daini no Jinsei wo Tannou suru you desu
Kishi Reijou wa Propose wo Kotowarenai
Kitae Sugite Konyaku Hakisareta Kekka, Kouri no Koushaku Kakka no Tsuma ni Nattakedo Jitsu wa Dekiaisareteiru you desu
Kojirase Outaishi to Yakusoku no Himegimi
Konyaku Hakisareta no ni Moto Konyakusha no Kekkonshiki ni Shoutaisaremashita. Kotowarenai no de Ani no Yuujin ni Doukou shite Moraimasu.
Akujo Reijou desu ga, Konyakusha no Amai Oshioki ni Kanaimasen
Akuyaku Reijou wa Mou Zenbu ga Iya ni Natta no de, Kioku Soushitsu no Furi wo suru Koto ni shita
Yotogi no Akujo - Hatsujou Taishitsu Reijou wa, Yorugoto Koutei ni Aisareru
Hakushaku-ke wo Mamoru Tame ni Toriaezu Konyakushimashita - Neet no Reijou wa Shuubun wo Harashi Ijiwaru na Koushaku-ke ni Taikou suru Tame Ichikabachika no Konyaku wo Ketsuden suru
Kon'yaku Haki 23-kai no Reiketsu Kikoushi wa Inaka no Ponkotsu Reijou ni Furimawasareru
Tensei shita Onna Mafia wa Isekai de Heibon ni Kurashitai - Asashin Ikka no Hakushaku Reijou desu ga, Denshi to Akuma na Danchou ga Tsukimatottekimasu
Narikin Reijou no Shiawase na Kekkon ~Kane no Mouja to Nonoshirareta Reijou wa Chichioya ni Urarete Henkyou no Buta Koushaku to Shiawase ni naru~
